# Project cost estimation

Environment variables for the frontend (create `.env` in project root):

```
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
```

Get these from your [Supabase](https://supabase.com) project → Settings → API.

Run the SQL migration in `supabase/migrations/001_initial_schema.sql` in the Supabase SQL editor to create tables and RLS policies.
